00:02:46.711 --> 00:02:48.110
and get some small furniture?

00:02:48.410 --> 00:02:49.710
Both of us are free

00:02:49.940 --> 00:02:51.040
this afternoon.

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:52.080
If you're free too,

00:02:52.730 --> 00:02:54.160
