can use the system

00:06:21.290 --> 00:06:22.250
for high-efficiency

00:06:22.250 --> 00:06:23.490
real-time control of lighting,

00:06:23.490 --> 00:06:24.880
heating, and cooling.

00:06:26.340 --> 00:06:26.830
Good.

00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:27.560
